布斯》</em></a> ，真人版“不是<em>《星际牛仔》</em> ”。无论如何，这并不重要，因为 Netflix 在 2021 年底<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/netflix-cowboy-bebop-canceled-000159745.html">取消了</a>该剧。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/adult-swim-lands-new-show-from-cowboy-bebop-and-john-wick-creators-161557849.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/adult-swim-lands-new-show-from-cowboy-bebop-and-john-wick-creators-161557849.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 583b256b-25a8-4096-9fc7-f86f5b2b2767</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jul 2023 16:15:57 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1689871991</ingested><modified> 2023-07-20T16:53:14+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/7d0839d0-271d-11ee-bffe-727b044faa1c" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/7d0839d0-271d-11ee-bffe-727b044faa1c" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Adult Swim]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A title card for the upcoming Adult Swim s